escape sequence for alignment
\n =new line
\t =tab (4 space)
\b=backspace
\0=null char
\r=overwritten
\"=double quotes
\'=single quotes
\\=single slash
jvm is used to covert the source file to bytes code
class Sample
{
public static void main(String args[])
{
System.out.println("ashika is a good \\n girl");
System.out.print("ashika is a good\b\b girl");
System.out.println("ashika \"is\" a good 'girl'");
System.out.println("ashika is a \\good ");
System.out.println("ashika is a \r good girl");
}
}

